        "text": "Not forsaken.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " St. Paul, like the author of the Epistle to the Hebrews, knew by blessed experience the truth of the promise, \"I will never leave thee nor forsake thee\" (",
