        "text": "). ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Cast down.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Flung to the ground, as in some lost battle; yet not doomed, not \"perishing.\" \"Though he fall, he shall not be utterly cast down, for the Lord upholdeth him with his hand\" (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Psalm 37:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). 2 Corinthians 4:9",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
